## ✅ What Was Tested

### 🔐 Authentication
- Login with JWT token
- Rejection of wrong/empty credentials
- Debug users endpoint

### 📊 Vendor Dashboard
- Auth protection (401 without token)
- `stats`, `topProducts`, `recentOrders`, `chart` keys all present and valid

### 📦 Vendor Products
- List own products (auth-scoped)
- Product search
- Create a new product (POST)
- Get product detail (GET by id)
- Update product (PATCH)
- Delete product (DELETE)
- Unauthenticated access blocked (401)

### 🛒 Vendor Orders
- List all orders (auth-scoped)
- Filter by: Pending, Processing, Dispatched, Completed

### 💰 Vendor Earnings
- Earnings overview (available, pending, lifetime, nextPayout)
- Transaction ledger list

### ⭐ Vendor Reviews
- Review list (auth-scoped to vendor's products)
- Metrics: avgRating, totalReviews, positive sentiment %

### 👤 Vendor Profile
- List vendor profiles
- Approve/Reject blocked for non-admin users (403/404)

### 📝 Vendor Registration
- Full vendor account registration (201)

### 🌐 Shared Endpoints
- Public products, categories, reviews accessible
- Orders, notifications, analytics accessible as vendor

### 🔒 Security
- All 5 vendor endpoints properly protected (401 without token)
- Tampered JWT token rejected (401)
- SQL injection in search handled safely (no 500)
- XSS in search handled safely (no 500)
- Long input strings handled safely (no 500)

